The paper deals with learning term-weighting schemes for text classification, which is a common problem in information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (ML) related to natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
